<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activate Your UnderNET CService Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="cid:logo" alt="UnderNET Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>Welcome to UnderNET CService</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Hello {{.Username}},</p>

    <p>Thank you for registering with UnderNET CService. To activate your account, please click the button below:</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{.ActivationURL}}" class="button">Activate Your Account</a>
    </div>

    <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="{{.ActivationURL}}">{{.ActivationURL}}</a></p>

    <p>Your activation link will expire in 48 hours. If you did not create this account, please ignore this email.</p>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{.Year}} UnderNET. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
